## 사용자 프로필 수정 API 구현 계획

### 1. GraphQL 스키마 정의

**위치**: `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/user.graphqls`

```graphql
input UpdateProfileInput {
    nickname: String
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    interests: [String!]
}

type UpdateProfileResult {
    userId: ID!
    nickname: String!
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    interests: [String!]!
    updatedAt: String!
}

extend type Mutation {
    updateProfile(input: UpdateProfileInput!): UpdateProfileResult!
}
```

---

### 2. GraphQL Controller

**위치**: `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/user/UserProfileController.kt`

```kotlin
@Controller
class UserProfileController(
    private val userProfileService: UserProfileService,
) {
    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun updateProfile(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument input: UpdateProfileInput,
    ): UpdateProfileResult {
        val response = userProfileService.updateProfile(userId, input)
        return response.toResult()
    }
}
```

---

### 3. GraphQL Service (gRPC Client)

**위치**: `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/user/UserProfileService.kt`

```kotlin
@Service
class UserProfileService {
    @GrpcClient("user-grpc")
    private lateinit var stub: UserServiceGrpc.UserServiceBlockingStub

    fun updateProfile(userId: String, input: UpdateProfileInput): UpdateProfileResponse {
        val request = UpdateProfileRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId(userId)
            .apply {
                input.nickname?.let { setNickname(it) }
                input.bio?.let { setBio(it) }
                input.profileImageUrl?.let { setProfileImageUrl(it) }
                input.interests?.let { addAllInterests(it) }
            }
            .build()
        return try {
            stub.updateProfile(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.trailers!!, e.status.description)
        }
    }
}
```

---

### 4. Proto 정의 (참고용)

**위치**: `protobuf/src/main/proto/user/user.proto`

```proto
message UpdateProfileRequest {
    string user_id = 1;
    optional string nickname = 2;
    optional string bio = 3;
    optional string profile_image_url = 4;
    repeated string interests = 5;
}

message UpdateProfileResponse {
    string user_id = 1;
    string nickname = 2;
    string bio = 3;
    string profile_image_url = 4;
    repeated string interests = 5;
    string updated_at = 6;
}

service UserService {
    // ...기존 메서드...
    rpc UpdateProfile(UpdateProfileRequest) returns (UpdateProfileResponse);
}
```

---

### 구현 순서 요약

| 단계 | 작업 | 위치 |
|------|------|------|
| 1 | Proto 메시지/메서드 추가 | `protobuf/` |
| 2 | `user` 서비스에 gRPC 핸들러 구현 | `user/` |
| 3 | GraphQL 스키마 작성 | `graphql/resources/graphql/` |
| 4 | GraphQL Service (gRPC 클라이언트) 작성 | `graphql/.../service/user/` |
| 5 | GraphQL Controller 작성 | `graphql/.../controller/user/` |
| 6 | 테스트 작성 (TDD) | 각 모듈 test 디렉토리 |

